<p>Welcome to my recipe journal, I'm Heidi. This is where I like to
write about the recipes that intersect my life, travels and interests.
I  write <a
href="http://www.amazon.com/exec/obidos/ASIN/1580082777/heidiswanson-20">cookbooks</a>,
love <a href="http://www.101cookbooks.com/build_a_natural/">natural
foods</a>, take lots of pictures, do a good amount of <a
href="http://101cookbooks.com/travel/">globetrotting</a>, and like to
make lists of <a href="/favorites_lists/">favorite things</a>.</p>
